-- European Union to Publish 2013 Cap for Its Carbon Permits Market Tomorrow
-- B y   E w a   K r u k o w s k a
-- 2010-10-21T08:56:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/european-commission-to-publish-2013-cap-for-its-carbon-market-tomorrow.html
The European Commission will
announce tomorrow the cap for 2013 emissions in its carbon
market including aluminum and chemical products makers that will
join the system in its next phase, the regulator said on its
website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
